    gated: false,
    content: "# Contact\n\n## Get in touch.\n\n---\n\n### General inquiries\nhello@asplenz.com\n\n### Sales and enterprise\nsales@asplenz.com\n\n### Support\nFor product support, open an issue on GitHub or email support@asplenz.com.\n\n---\n\n### Want a demo?\n\nSee Knowledge in action with your team's data. We'll walk through extraction, enforcement, and agent integration in 30 minutes.\n\n[Schedule a demo](mailto:sales@asplenz.com?subject=Knowledge%20Demo%20Request)\n\n---\n\n### Office\n\nAsplenz\nParis, France\n",
